<troubleshooting id="troubleshooting-1172" xml:lang="en-us" class="- topic/topic troubleshooting/troubleshooting "><title class="- topic/title ">Timed out waiting for the driver server to start</title><troublebody class="- topic/body troubleshooting/troublebody "><condition class="- topic/section troubleshooting/condition "><p class="- topic/p ">Timed out waiting for the driver server to start.</p></condition><troubleSolution class="- topic/bodydiv troubleshooting/troubleSolution "><remedy class="- topic/section troubleshooting/remedy "><steps class="- topic/ol task/steps "><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Download the correct Edge driver from the Microsoft website here: <xref format="html" href="https://developer.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-edge/tools/webdriver/" scope="external" class="- topic/xref ">Microsoft Edge Driver </xref>based on your OS build (Go to <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Start</b> &gt; <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Settings</b> &gt; <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">System</b> &gt; <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">About</b> and locate the number next to OS Build on the screen).</cmd></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Copy downloaded Edge driver and replace it in existing <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">edgedriver</codeph> folder of <ph conkeyref="name-variables/katalon-studio" class="- topic/ph "/>. For example: <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">C:\\Katalon\_Studio\_Windows_64-4.8\\configuration\\resources\\drivers\\edgedriver</codeph>.</cmd></step></steps></remedy></troubleSolution></troublebody></troubleshooting>